{"tid":2485412,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"麻枝准首部小說作品『貓狩り族の長（狩貓族族長）』將於5月17日發售","createTime":"2021-04-12T08:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T23:13:29.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"20632680dab81c1d798c47259b4652e1cab5b392","tid":2485412,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"麻枝准的首部小說作品『貓狩り族の長（狩貓族族長）』將於5月17日由講談社在日本出版發行！<br />\n<br />\n一位是被貓嫌棄又想去死的天才作曲家，一位是一無所有的大學生。<br />\n這是一則屬於這難以互相理解的二人的、即使無法心意相通也仍然溫暖的故事。<br />\n<br />\n販售店鋪的連結將依次公開。敬請期待。<br />\n<br />\n▼官方網站▼<br />\n<a href=\"https://key.visualarts.gr.jp/nekogari/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkey.visualarts.gr.jp%2Fnekogari%2F&d=uTsTvEvhFTFW0ksY74cvWgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=9f69ace0\" target=\"_blank\">https://key.visualarts.gr.jp/nekogari/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/key_official/status/1381517610458570754?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkey_official%2Fstatus%2F1381517610458570754%3Fs%3D21&d=uTsTvEvhFTFW0ksY74cvWgpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=30234b4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkey_official%2Fstatus%2F1381517610458570754%3Fs%3D21&h=d01f94d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/key_official/status/1381517610458570754?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"014e2fd479ab2816d501a887fa9cd991852c2bd1","tid":2485412,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"原來呢條on9冇寫過小說-.-"},{"pid":"dcb67470b0888a3085d4bb14116fa68737515fd3","tid":2485412,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"014e2fd479ab2816d501a887fa9cd991852c2bd1","tid":2485412,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"原來呢條on9冇寫過小說-.-"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T08:49:08.000Z","msg":"請尊重-.-"},{"pid":"230938632893db832973e0124a63e0586423e4d1","tid":2485412,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"